{"type": "article", "id": 26208, "title": "“悬浮”椅背的座椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-29T07:23:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162023hj9XCA5YQDBt0EM4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">由奥地利设计师 <a href=\"http://www.frankrettenbacher.com/\">Frank Rettenbacher</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.zanotta.it/en/\">ZANOTTA</a> 所设计 June 系列是一组椅背看上去像是悬浮在座位上的椅子——也就是说，你看不到连接处。</p>\n<p class=\"\">设计环节中最大的挑战就是如何让椅背不借助可见的螺丝钉，同时又要与座位接合在一起，Rettenbacher 在和技术团队经过激烈的沟通之后，最终确定了现在所看到的这种隐蔽的接合方法。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162020lVU2fG3FQHgvKh9p.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162021p1e0XBEz63tK5DMa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162021wZ8cWDbP51AvQmNj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021620221SLtvehysHPGJXnR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}